00:00:50,323 --> 00:00:52,124
on the rights and lefts
of the choreography,

32
00:00:52,158 --> 00:00:54,627
and I've recruited three hot
Cheerios! to get us to 12...

33
00:00:54,661 --> 00:00:57,696
You don't have to prove
yourself to me, Sam.

34
