All right, I like this plan,

140
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,854
and I love that you guys like my songs.

141
00:05:56,888 --> 00:05:59,156
So, yes, I'll write for
the artists on your label.

142
00:05:59,191 --> 00:06:01,358
