(chuckles) Uh...

222
00:09:16,066 --> 00:09:17,399
I'll tell you one thing.

223
00:09:17,434 --> 00:09:19,702
I think, uh, Accounting Club
interferes with Glee Club.

224
00:09:21,571 --> 00:09:23,506
Marley, are you planning
on quitting Glee Club?

225
00:09:26,977 --> 00:09:29,078
I didn't want to let anyone down.

226
00:09:30,981 --> 00:09:33,816
And since this is going to be my swan song,

227
00:09:33,850 --> 00:09:35,651
I just want it to be fun.

228
00:09:35,685 --> 00:09:37,820
So, please, don't tell anyone.

229
00:09:41,625 --> 00:09:44,193
Are you sure we should be doing this?

230
00:09:44,227 --> 00:09:45,554
I mean, if we get caught...

231
00:09:45,564 --> 00:09:46,564
Oh, just go!

232
00:09:46,598 --> 00:09:48,332
Trust me, when I was in the Warblers,

233
00:09:48,367 --> 00:09:50,501
sneaking onto stage the night
before a show was tradition.

234
00:09:50,535 --> 00:09:52,837
We had other traditions, but
I can't really speak of them.

235
00:09:52,871 --> 00:09:54,171
We're not doing anything wrong.

236
00:09:54,206 --> 00:09:55,706
We're just, you know, getting a feel

237
00:09:55,741 --> 00:09:57,441
for the layout of the stage... our stage.

238
00:09:57,476 --> 00:09:59,777
So should we sing a song or hold hands

239
00:09:59,811 --> 00:10:01,212
or say a prayer or something?

240
00:10:01,246 --> 00:10:02,413
Because if I'm being honest,

241
00:10:02,447 --> 00:10:04,115
this ghost light's kind of freaking me out.

242
00:10:04,149 --> 00:10:06,250
All right, everybody,
circle up. I have a surprise.

243
00:10:09,254 --> 00:10:13,324
Finn Hudson made us a promise
at the beginning of the year:

244
00:10:13,358 --> 00:10:16,794
that we were all going
back to nationals together.

245
00:10:16,828 --> 00:10:18,629
Even when we lost sectionals,

246
00:10:18,663 --> 00:10:21,999
which was totally not Marley's fault,

247
00:10:22,034 --> 00:10:23,801
Finn told us that it wasn't over.

248
00:10:23,835 --> 00:10:27,605
He said that we'd be right here, together.

